post_text:
All middle school students are encouraged to come to the middle school on their assigned date from 9:00 a.m. - 3:00 p.m. to put school supplies in their lockers, find out where their classes are, and talk to staff members. For the health and safety of our students and staff, we are asking that only students enter the buildings.

6th Grade: Tuesday, August 25;
7th Grade: Wednesday, August 26;
8th Grade: Thursday, August 27.
9:00 a.m. - 3:00 p.m. each day.

